# Local Ports (Operator-specific) — DO NOT COMMIT REAL VALUES

This file is a local operator note. Copy to:
  docs/local/ports.local.md

## Example
- Public domain: https://example.myfritz.link
- Fritzbox port forwards:
  - WAN 443 -> nexus-edge:443
  - WAN 80  -> nexus-edge:80 (optional / ACME)
- Edge (nexus-edge):
  - 443/80 public
  - 22 LAN-only
  - 53 LAN-only (Pi-hole)
- Core (nexus-core):
  - 22 LAN-only
  - n8n: 127.0.0.1:5678 (NOT exposed)
  - openclaw: 127.0.0.1:PORT (NOT exposed)
